  <text>
    Neutronium-doped Wafer, an advanced wafer material.
  </text> 
  <br/>
  <h3>Source</h3>
  <text>
    Neutronium-doped Wafers are produced by cutting <style color="0xafff00" underlined="true" link="gtceu:circuits/neutronium_boule" hover-info="click link">Neutronium-doped monocrystalline Silicon Boule</style> in a <style color="0xafff00" underlined="true" link="gtceu:machines/cutter" hover-info="click link">cutter</style> at the lowest IV-Tier voltage. 
    <br/>
    (<style color="0xafff00" underlined="true" link="gtceu:multiblock/cleanroom" hover-info="click link">Cleanroom</style> is required)
  </text>
  <recipe id="gtceu:cutter/cut_neutronium_boule_water"/>
  <br/>
  <h3>Usage</h3>
  <text left-margin="10">
    - Neutronium-doped Wafers can be used to produce wafers instead of <style color="0xafff00" underlined="true" link="gtceu:circuits/silicon_wafer" hover-info="click link">silicon wafers</style> in a <style color="0xafff00" underlined="true" link="gtceu:machines/laser_engraver" hover-info="click link">Laser Engraver</style>, which can increase the yield up to <style color="0xff5555">16 times</style>.
    <br/>
    <br/>
    - Neutronium-doped Wafers can be used to produce wafers instead of <style color="0xafff00" underlined="true" link="gtceu:circuits/phosphorus_wafer" hover-info="click link">phosphorus wafers</style> in a <style color="0xafff00" underlined="true" link="gtceu:machines/laser_engraver" hover-info="click link">Laser Engraver</style>, which can increase the yield up to <style color="0xff5555">8 times</style>.
    <br/>
    <br/>
    - Neutronium-doped Wafers can be used to produce wafers instead of <style color="0xafff00" underlined="true" link="gtceu:circuits/naquadah_wafer" hover-info="click link">naquadah wafers</style> in a <style color="0xafff00" underlined="true" link="gtceu:machines/laser_engraver" hover-info="click link">Laser Engraver</style>, which can increase the yield up to <style color="0xff5555">4 times</style>.
    <br/>
    <br/>
